Test Steps:
1. Select test-suite in Q7 Explorer
2. Choose "Q7/Add Tag..." from context menu
3. Enter tag and press "Ok" button
4. Make sure that new tag is added in Tags view
5. Make sure that tag is added in test-suite editor
